+- **`tests/core/delegate.test.ts`** (integration, synthetic multi-hop): build an agent whose `tools` include an `asDelegateTool` wrapping another agent. Drive (via `withRootDelegationContext(knownCtx, â€¦)` to set a known caller budget): (a) over-depth chain â†’ deep `execute` returns soft `{error}` + `agent.guardrail.violation` event (assert via `registerTestProvider()` InMemory exporter); (b) a long specialist return â†’ truncated to `returnCapChars(knownCtx)` with the marker; (c) within-depth recursive re-entry of the same agent succeeds. Use `MockLanguageModelV3`.
